    class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover rounded-xl"
  />
</div>

<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  Frame your face with perfectly shaped brows. Our expert eyebrow waxing service in Phoenix delivers precise, symmetrical results that enhance your natural features.
</p>

