    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">3.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Precision Waxing</strong> — Using gentle hard wax, we remove unwanted hairs with precision.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">4.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Finishing</strong> — We tweeze any stray hairs and apply soothing post-wax care.
