        <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2 text-lg">✓</span>
        <span><strong>Finer regrowth</strong> — Regular waxing can make hair grow back finer over time</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2 text-lg">✓</span>
        <span><strong>Quick service</strong> — In and out in 15 minutes</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_886dc122-ff4a-498f-b95b-3e99986eb926_sleek-eyebrow-shape.webp"
