<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ul class="space-y-2">
    <li>• Let your brows grow out for at least 2-3 weeks for best shaping results</li>
    <li>• Avoid retinol or exfoliating products 5-7 days before</li>
    <li>• Come with clean skin (no makeup on brows)</li>
    <li>• Bring reference photos if you have a specific shape in mind</li>
  </ul>
</div>

